  <text>
      <body>
         <div type="edition"><ab>
<lb n="1"/>  بسم اللّه الرّحمن الرّحيم 
<lb n="2"/>  ادفع إلى بديح 
<lb n="3"/>  لأحمد الغلام 
<lb n="4"/>  الّذي وجّهنا به 
<lb n="5"/>  مع <app type="BL"><lem resp="Diem">الحمّار </lem><rdg resp="Diem">الحمّار</rdg></app> إلى 
<lb n="6"/>  ‮البدرمون ‪γʹ‬ 
<lb n="7"/>  ‮في <app type="BL"><lem resp="APD"><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">يوم</unclear> </lem><rdg resp="Diem. sīn with dash">مسريه</rdg></app> ‪ιϑ‬ 
<lb n="8"/>  <app type="BL"><lem resp="APD">الجمعة </lem><rdg resp="Diem">÷</rdg></app> 
</ab></div>
         <div type="edition"><ab>
 <lb n="1"/>bi smi ăl lāhi ăr raḥmāni ăr raḥīmi 
 <lb n="2"/>ĭdfaʿ ʾilà budayḥa 
 <lb n="3"/>li ʾaḥmada ăl ġulāmi 
 <lb n="4"/>ăllaḏī waǧǧahnā bi hi 
 <lb n="5"/>maʿa ăl ḥammāri ḥimāri ʾilà 
 <lb n="6"/>ăl badramūni ‪1/3 
 <lb n="7"/>fī yawmi misrīha ‪19 
 <lb n="8"/>ăl 1/3 ǧumʿaẗi ø 
  </ab></div>
<div type="translation"><ab>
			<lb n="1"/>
		In the name of God, the Compassionate, the Merciful.
			<lb n="2"/>
		Hand over to Budaiḥ
			<lb n="3"/>
		on behalf of Aḥmad, the groom,
			<lb n="4"/>
		whom we have sent
			<lb n="5"/>
		with the ass to
		zusammen mit dem Eseltreiber
			<lb n="6"/>
		al-Badramûn 1/3
			<lb n="7"/>
		(Geschrieben) am 19. Mesori.
		on Fri- 19th
			<lb n="8"/>
		1/3 (Dinar)
		day
</ab></div>
